				<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: 13.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left" align="left">
				<b>
				<span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: #0643cc; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">“</span><span style="COLOR: #0643cc; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">康乐家园</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: #0643cc; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">”</span><span style="COLOR: #0643cc; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">网会员服务模式</span></b></p>
				<p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 13.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left" align="left">
				<span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">“</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">康乐家园</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">”</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">网是为肝病病人提供的医疗服务模式如下图示：</span></p>
				<img border="0" src="image/serv_flow.GIF" width="605" height="457"><p class="MsoNormal">　</p>
				<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">注意：</span><span lang="EN-US">1</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">、住院出院病人是康乐家园病人管理的起点，只对住院后出院的病人，提供规范化方案，并跟踪随访。住院病人，再次门诊随访时，可以与他的主管医生联系，由主管医生指导随访。</span></p>
				<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">、单纯门诊病人（没有住过院的病人），病人按门诊医生的门诊意见执行。不在康乐家园另外提供规范化方案。但是该病人可以免费享受网上咨询，自己健康日志记录，健康教育。</span></p>
				<p class="MsoNormal"><b>
				<span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: #0643cc; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">“</span><span style="COLOR: #0643cc; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">康乐家园</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: #0643cc; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">”</span><span style="COLOR: #0643cc; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">网会员服务内容</span></b></p>
				<p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 13.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left" align="left">
				<span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">
				依据上述医疗服务模式，考虑到满足会员对不同层次服务的需求。我们采取会员制管理，提供两种会员级别，普通会员（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">“</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">互佑</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">”</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">卡）：免费，会员享受基本服务；超值会员（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">“</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">平安</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">”</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">卡）：收费，会员除享受基本服务外，更提供专属服务。会员身份可随时办理转换。</span></p>
				<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: 13.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align="center">
				<img border="0" src="image/serv_content.JPG" width="312" height="151"></p>
				<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: 13.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left" align="left">
				<b>
				<span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: #0002c4; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">“</span><span style="COLOR: #0002c4; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">互佑</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: #0002c4; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">”</span><span style="COLOR: #0002c4; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">卡（普通会员卡）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: #0002c4; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><br>
				</span></b><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">
				免费，加入康乐家园的病人获赠佑安康乐家园</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">“</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">互佑</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">”</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">卡，是佑安医院为肝病病友提供健康跟踪咨询服务的会员卡，采用实名制，仅限会员本人使用，不得转借。</span></p>
				<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: 13.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left" align="left">
				<span style="COLOR: #0002c4; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">【可享受的会员服务】</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: #0002c4; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><br>
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">　　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">1.
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">
				个人电子健康档案的登记和维护。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">
				<br>
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">　　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">2.
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">定期随访提醒和通知服务。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><br>
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">　　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">3.
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">
				网上咨询：无限次不点名邀请佑安联盟医院的主管医生对病情进行远程咨询。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><br>
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">　　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">4.
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">
				定期收到与健康相关的电子邮件；定期参加健康教育活动。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><br>
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">　　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">5.
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">
				预约住院：免费享受预约住院。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><br>
				<br>
				　</span></p>
				<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: 13.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left" align="left">
				<b>
				<span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: #0002c4; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">“</span><span style="COLOR: #0002c4; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">平安</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: #0002c4; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">”</span><span style="COLOR: #0002c4; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">卡（超值会员卡）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: #0002c4; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">:<br>
				</span></b><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">
				收费，是佑安医院为加入康乐家园的肝病病友在普通卡服务基础上提供系列增值服务的超值会员卡。采用实名制，仅限会员本人使用，不得转借。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">“</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">平安</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">”</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">卡不单纯是为了方便病友看病而建立的服务体系，更是为了让病友得到佑安医院专家最高标准的健康跟踪管理，是佑安医院主动服务病友，帮助病友把紧迫被动浪费时间的就医过程转变成重要而从容的防病过程，防患于未然，保障健康。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">“</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">平安</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">”</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">卡会员除享受普通会员服务内容之外，更享受系列增值服务。</span></p>
				<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 26.25pt; TEXT-INDENT: -26.25pt">
				<span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">【可享受的会员服务】</span><span lang="EN-US"><br>
				</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">普通会员服务：</span><span lang="EN-US">
				</span></p>
				<p class="MsoNormal">
				<span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">　　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black">1.
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">
				个人电子健康档案的登记和维护。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black">
				<br>
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">　　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black">2.
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">定期随访提醒和通知服务。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black"><br>
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">　　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black">3.
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">
				网上咨询：无限次不点名邀请佑安联盟医院的主管医生对病情进行远程咨询。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black"><br>
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">　　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black">4.
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">
				定期收到与健康相关的电子邮件；定期参加健康教育活动。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black"><br>
				</span><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">　　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black">5.
